# React Islands

Use React only where Astro cannot: menus with state, search, Strapi Blocks renderer.

## Location

- `src/components/islands/` — interactive UI (MobileMenu, ArticleSearch, ArticleContent)
- `src/components/widgets/SiWidget.tsx` — SI embed wrapper

## Rules

- Default export, functional components, `react` hooks only
- Props passed from parent `.astro` file — keep islands dumb where possible
- Use `className` (Tailwind), not Astro `class`
- **Never** import `@/lib/si/client`, `@/lib/mailgun`, or Strapi client — server-only
- Brand colours via Tailwind (`text-ab-green`) or inline styles matching tokens

## Hydration

Parent Astro file controls when JS loads:

```astro
<ArticleContent content={article.content} strapiUrl={STRAPI_URL} client:load />
```

Prefer `client:load` for above-the-fold interactivity; `client:visible` for below-fold if added later.

## Vite alias note

New island files need an explicit alias in `astro.config.mjs` if imported without extension in SSR builds. Follow existing entries for `ArticleContent`, `MobileMenu`, etc.
